The paper proposes a method for detecting anomalies in heterogeneous information networks, which involves tensor decomposition and clustering methods. This topic is relevant to several sub-categories in computer science, including social and information networks (cs.SI), information retrieval (cs.IR), databases (cs.DB), machine learning (cs.LG), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
